resource.description:
Tests exporting packages, updating. &lt;BR&gt;Tests
 what happens when a bundle is updated and exports another
 package.&lt;BR&gt;Tests Bundle.getResource().&lt;BR&gt;

Tests lifecycle operations: &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;pre&gt;
 testNormalInstallStartStopUninstall   Normal lifecycles&lt;br&gt;
 testStartStopWithException            Check exception handling&lt;br&gt;
