 testBrokenStream                      Stream that breaks&lt;br&gt;
 testEvents                            Event sequences&lt;br&gt;
 testServiceRegistrations              Registering services&lt;br&gt;
 testNormalUpdate                      Updating normal&lt;br&gt;
 testRollbackUpdate                    Check rollback&lt;br&gt;
 testStoppedBundleContext              Stopped bundle&lt;br&gt;
 testGetLocation                       Location handling&lt;br&gt;
 tests that securityExceptions are thrown in Bundle methods&lt;br&gt;
 tests that securityExceptions are thrown in BundleContext
 methods&lt;br&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;br&gt;

The following tests are executed&lt;br&gt; &lt;pre&gt;
  Tests the synchronous bundle listener&lt;br&gt; 
 Tests that synchrounousBundleListener can't be added without&lt;br&gt;
  admin permision&lt;br&gt;  Tests that listeners can
 be registered multiple times&lt;br&gt;  Tests if a
 listener can catch events from it's own bundle&lt;br&gt;
  Tests if SynchronousBundleListener is synchronous&lt;br&gt;
  Tests if SynchronousBundleListeners are called prior to BundleListeners&lt;br&gt;
	 &lt;/pre&gt;

